Package: CEOdata
Title: Datasets of the CEO (Centre d'Estudis d'Opinio) for Opinion Polls in Catalonia
Version: 1.2.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Xavier", "Fernández-i-Marín", , "xavier.fim@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9522-8870"))
Description: Easy and convenient access to the datasets of the
  "Centre d'Estudis d'Opinio", the Catalan institution for polling and public
  opinion. The package uses the data stored in the servers of the CEO and returns
  it in a tidy format.
Depends:
  R (>= 4.1.0),
  haven,
  dplyr (>= 1.0.0),
  urltools,
  stringr,
  jsonlite
Suggests:
  knitr,
  R.rsp,
  ggplot2,
  tidyr (> 1.1.1),
  curl,
  rmarkdown,
  vtable,
  compareGroups
License: GPL-3
URL: https://ceo.gencat.cat/ca/inici/, https://github.com/ceopinio/CEOdata/
BugReports: https://github.com/ceopinio/CEOdata/issues/
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.0
VignetteBuilder: knitr, R.rsp
